verbose_text: Further nucleophilic attack of the nitroso oxygen aided by the protonation of the new C =O group enable the facile 1,3-shift of the cationic CHOHCONH 2 + unit, which is -22.0 kcal / mol exergonic over a low free energy barrier of 10.9 kcal / mol (via TSK +).
